- Minibox -

Small Linux commands for resource limited systems

Copyright (C) 2017-2021 Ercan Ersoy

This software is licensed under GNU General Public License version 2 and
GNU General Public License version 3.


-- Thanks --

Thanks to Berki YenigÅn for French translations.


-- Compiling --

The Minibox program must be compiled with GCC.


--- MS-DOS, FreeDOS etc. ---

You must use DJGPP.

You should compile with the command line given below.

    make dos


-- Usage --

    MINIBOX Command [Arguments]
    MINIBOX --help|--version


-- Commands --

  * beep
  * cat
  * cd
  * clear
  * cp
  * date
  * echo
  * help
  * ls
  * mkdir
  * mv
  * pwd
  * rm
  * rmdir
  * sh
  * time


